00:31:01,209 --> 00:31:04,900
<i>1. Više puta ponoviti plan putovanja</i>

401
00:31:07,506 --> 00:31:12,369
2. Popisati stavke po
prioritetima

402
00:31:12,470 --> 00:31:13,812
<i>Osam pari gaća.</i>

403
00:31:13,971 --> 00:31:15,372
<i>Dva šestara.</i>

404
00:31:15,473 --> 00:31:16,915
<i>Tri tamnocrvena pulovera.</i>

405
00:31:17,016 --> 00:31:19,819
<i>Termometar
hidrometar, barometar.</i>

